  "texts": [
    "The study was approved by the university's ethics review committee.",
    "Pilot StudyWe invited six participants who are interested in using AI to manage their emotional well-being to interact with ChatLab on a daily basis for a week.",
    "The participants were all university students (three undergraduate and three graduate), and three of them had prior experiences with LLMs.",
    "Next, they joined a two-hour focus group to share their experience with ChatLab.",
    "Their participation was voluntary without compensation.Overall, participants created distinctive personas on ChatLab (e.g., a famous King in history or a virtual lover) and found the conversations engaging."
  ],
